    Execute Command    nvm_ctrl InjectPartialWrite 0x10000000
    ${word}=           Execute Command    sysbus ReadQuadWord 0x10000000
    Should Not Be Equal As Numbers    ${word}    0xA1A2A3A4A5A6A7A8

